give you back the keys to the Cruiser?

00:14.047 --> 00:15.981
You know,
so we could actually...

00:16.049 --> 00:17.983
leave the property?

00:19.285 --> 00:21.753
I don't know. Maybe never.

00:21.821 --> 00:24.756
