talkin' about this.

00:50.083 --> 00:52.017
How long to the curfew?

00:52.085 --> 00:54.519
Uh, about one minute.

00:54.587 --> 00:56.782
Now, Donna,
I'm not bragging, but...

00:56.856 --> 01:00.053
