actually do it in that amount of time.

01:01.361 --> 01:03.921
You don't have to tell me.

01:03.997 --> 01:06.022
Okay, so...

01:06.099 --> 01:10.433
Buckle up, Donna, 'cause the next...
12 seconds are all about you, babe.

01:10.503 --> 01:12.437
<i>Five, four...</i>

01:12.505 --> 01:14.496
- three, two, one.
- No, wait. But I... Damn.

01:14.574 --> 01:15.939
Curfew, hophead.

