02:30.483 --> 02:32.417
These boys, they need structure.

02:32.485 --> 02:34.453
Well, I'll see ya.

02:34.521 --> 02:36.648
Where do you think you're going?

02:36.723 --> 02:39.317
To... night church?

02:42.795 --> 02:44.729
Sorry, honey.
Curfew's for everyone.

02:45.865 --> 02:48.527
But, Daddy, it's me!

02:50.136 --> 02:52.661
Look, what they did is bad...

02:52.739 --> 02:56.732
but you sneakin' around with Kelso,
that's just... unpleasant.

02:57.810 --> 03:00.711
But, Daddy,
I'm not seeing Kelso.

03:00.780 --> 03:03.044
- Untrue!
- A damnable lie!

03:06.052 --> 03:07.986
A curfew?

03:08.054 --> 03:11.217
I'm stuck in this house
with you people all night? This sucks!

03:11.291 --> 03:14.158
Well, we're just
<i>thrilled</i> about it.

03:14.227 --> 03:16.957
All right. There's an upside to all this.
I took her down with me.

03:17.030 --> 03:18.964
- Nice job.
- Thanks.

03:22.669 --> 03:25.103
Well, isn't this a happy house?

03:26.172 --> 03:28.163
Yeah.

03:32.645 --> 03:35.478
This is <i>not</i> a happy house.

03:35.548 --> 03:37.778
Well, you just said
this was a happy house.

03:38.985 --> 03:41.681
Well, that's not what I meant.
It was sarcasm.

03:41.754 --> 03:45.281
Who the hell knows what you mean,
when you won't say what you mean?

03:49.028 --> 03:51.121
I don't like how you're
treating the children.

03:51.197 --> 03:53.859
Look, Kitty.

03:53.933 --> 03:57.562
I'm not gonna let our kids
go down the wrong path.

03:57.637 --> 04:01.596
- But if you have a better idea, I'm all ears.
- Okay.

04:01.674 --> 04:06.043
Maybe you could be a little less strict
and a little more loving.

04:12.619 --> 04:15.053
Okay, Kitty.
Enough with the sarcasm.

04:24.931 --> 04:27.957
Stop looking at me.
Stop looking at me. Stop looking at me.

04:29.636 --> 04:33.629
