ate somethin' off the floor.

05:46.212 --> 05:50.239
Okay, well, um...
Your father's gonna drive me to work.

05:50.316 --> 05:53.251
That's right. And if you do
anything wrong, I'll know...

05:53.319 --> 05:56.447
because one of you is a snitch.

05:56.522 --> 06:00.515
<i>You just think about that</i>
<i>while I'm gone.</i>

06:00.593 --> 06:02.720
Well, they're not gonna do
anything wrong...

06:02.795 --> 06:07.095
because I brought a box of activities
to occupy their time.

06:07.166 --> 06:11.364
So, um... Be good and have fun.

06:11.437 --> 06:13.564
Do crafts, not drugs!

06:16.676 --> 06:18.610
Ooh, a model airplane and glue.

06:32.658 --> 06:34.751
Where's Steven and Eric?

06:34.827 --> 06:38.490
Um... Your hair is very pretty.

06:40.700 --> 06:42.998
Oh, they can't leave the house.
They're grounded.

06:43.069 --> 06:45.367
Oh, don't worry about them.
They're at The Hub.

06:47.573 --> 06:50.269
Oh, no. I am the snitch.

06:50.343 --> 06:53.244
Oh, Red is gonna be furious.

06:53.312 --> 06:55.872
Mrs. Forman, may I tell you
a little story about oppression?

06:57.650 --> 06:59.584
Okay.

07:02.321 --> 07:05.017
Once I had an ant farm.

07:05.091 --> 07:07.218
And they would not
build their tunnels.

07:08.861 --> 07:12.627
I was furious, so I became
very strict and stern with my ants.

07:14.200 --> 07:16.930
First they feared me,
and everything was fine...

07:17.003 --> 07:20.461
but eventually the ants
broke out and attacked me.

07:24.744 --> 07:27.474
So I had to kill them.

07:29.382 --> 07:32.180
So, um, you think we're being
too hard on the kids?

07:33.352 --> 07:35.286
Well, I don't know about that.

07:35.354 --> 07:38.755
