I'm really sad because my ants are dead.

07:40.993 --> 07:43.587
Okay. Well, Fez, thanks.

07:45.231 --> 07:47.222
You're a good boy.

07:49.101 --> 07:51.626
All the ladies want a piece of Fez.

07:56.008 --> 07:57.942
What are you doing?

07:58.010 --> 08:00.604
Oh, just a little
security measure...

08:00.680 --> 08:03.274
in case anybody tries to escape.

08:03.349 --> 08:08.582
Red, no. Those are my Christmas bells.
Those are happy bells.

08:10.423 --> 08:12.721
Well, then they're
doing their job...

08:12.792 --> 08:14.726
because I'm happy.

08:15.862 --> 08:17.830
Let's have some cake.

08:17.897 --> 08:23.631
