And welcome to
<i>The Forman Bunch Variety Hour.</i>

11:07.633 --> 11:13.128
And, boy, do we have
a great show for you tonight.

11:13.205 --> 11:16.504
Sorry, Mom.
We can't stay for the show.

11:16.575 --> 11:19.442
