11:52.044 --> 11:54.604
Don't worry, Kitty.
I'll take care of them.

11:56.682 --> 12:02.643
Ladies and gentlemen,
star of stage and screen, Shirley Jones.

12:07.226 --> 12:08.887
Hi, Mom.

12:08.961 --> 12:12.294
- Mom?
- That's right, Kitty.

12:12.364 --> 12:15.663
- We're Partridges now.
- This is gonna be great.

12:15.735 --> 12:18.260
I'm pretty sure
I can nail Susan Dey.

12:23.142 --> 12:25.667
No. Partridges?

12:25.745 --> 12:29.442
You can't live in a bus.
There's no toilet.

12:29.515 --> 12:35.351
Well, it may be inconvenient, Kitty, but
we do get to spend a lot of time together.

12:35.421 --> 12:38.720
That's right. Mrs. Partridge quit her job
to form a family band.

12:38.791 --> 12:41.021
Yep. It's all a matter
of choices, Kitty.

12:41.093 --> 12:44.585
I guess you just
chose to be a bad mother.

12:46.632 --> 12:50.227
Hey, Shirley. Can I come?
I play the tambourine.

12:50.302 --> 12:55.205
Oh, I'm sorry, Laurie.
No whores on my show.

12:56.942 --> 12:59.672
Oh, fine. Hey, Shields. Wait up!

13:06.018 --> 13:08.646
Aaah! Cuchi-cuchi-cuchi!

13:08.721 --> 13:11.747
- Whoa, whoa...
- Can it, Charo.

13:11.824 --> 13:13.815
Yeah!

13:17.563 --> 13:19.622
Well, I am not gonna
let that happen.

13:23.402 --> 13:26.963
Oh, no. This <i>is</i> crap.

13:47.225 --> 13:49.193
Oh, no. Honey.

13:50.629 --> 13:52.563
