he could sneak out.

13:52.631 --> 13:56.158
So. What now, Ho Chi Minh?

13:56.234 --> 13:59.897
Well, I'll tell you one thing.
Playtime is over.

13:59.971 --> 14:02.371
Your friends are no longer
allowed in the house.

14:02.440 --> 14:06.103
- Wait. What?
- No, no. We'll talk about it in the morning.

14:06.177 --> 14:08.839
Fine, we'll talk about it
in the morning.

14:10.949 --> 14:14.316
We'll talk about how your friends
are no longer allowed in the house.

14:16.454 --> 14:19.912
You know,
I have an interesting idea.

14:19.991 --> 14:22.186
Why don't
we <i>not</i> punish him?

14:22.260 --> 14:26.253
Why don't we try a little of that forgiveness
that Jesus was always talking about?

14:32.404 --> 14:36.670
No, no.
This is for his own good.

14:36.741 --> 14:39.972
Look, in order for Eric to be
a happy, well-adjusted adult...

14:40.045 --> 14:42.411
he has to be miserable now.

14:43.548 --> 14:46.415
That's just good parenting.

14:46.484 --> 14:48.509
If I was to be
Mr. Nice Guy now...

14:48.587 --> 14:51.613
do you know what would happen
to Eric in a few years?

14:51.690 --> 14:54.420
Do you?

14:54.492 --> 14:56.960
Oh, Eric. Breakfast.

15:03.335 --> 15:05.895
Well, there's
my sweet little baby boy.

15:08.306 --> 15:11.434
Why oh why
didn't I discipline you?

15:11.509 --> 15:13.602
Shut up and eat your cornflakes.

15:19.818 --> 15:22.309
That's what.

15:22.387 --> 15:27.381
Never surrender, Kitty.
Never retreat. We're winning.

15:27.459 --> 15:31.054
The fact that Eric was desperate enough
to climb out his window...

15:31.129 --> 15:33.529
shows that
everything is working.

15:42.207 --> 15:43.697
Surprise.

15:45.110 --> 15:49.444
This is so great.
I didn't... know you delivered.

15:51.549 --> 15:53.483
<i>Bed check, dumb-ass.</i>

15:53.551 --> 15:55.485
Holy crap.

15:56.788 --> 15:59.086
No, it is not a bed check.

15:59.157 --> 16:01.091
We just wanna say good night...

16:01.159 --> 16:03.923
and... and we love you very, very much.

16:03.995 --> 16:06.589
What are you doing?

16:06.665 --> 16:08.599
Oh, just nailing
his window shut.

16:09.868 --> 16:12.962
