17:00.919 --> 17:03.149
Oh. Hi, Daddy.

17:04.155 --> 17:06.146
Sorry to bother you, kitten.

17:11.195 --> 17:14.256
Kelso, get your hand off my ass.

17:14.332 --> 17:16.266
- It was an accident.
- Shh!

17:16.334 --> 17:19.770
- It's still there.
- It's still an accident.

17:19.838 --> 17:21.829
- Kelso, it's still there!
- Yeah.

17:24.041 --> 17:26.101
You know, Steven...

17:26.176 --> 17:30.511
this hatred thing you have for me
is just you protecting yourself.

17:30.582 --> 17:32.914
- Okay.
- It's true.

17:32.984 --> 17:34.918
You're afraid to reach
the peaks of love...

17:34.986 --> 17:37.045
for fear of
being dropped off a cliff.

17:40.458 --> 17:42.790
Well, I'm your
safety line, Steven.

17:44.062 --> 17:46.929
So grab me.

17:48.032 --> 17:49.966
Go grab yourself, freak.

17:52.036 --> 17:54.231
<i>Okay, bed check. Here we come.</i>

17:54.305 --> 17:56.603
- Get out!
- <i>Kitty, you're warning him.</i>

17:56.674 --> 17:59.438
<i>I'm not warning anybody. Getting closer!</i>

18:02.947 --> 18:04.881
Okay, um...

18:04.949 --> 18:07.008
We just... We wanted to say good night...

18:07.085 --> 18:09.019
<i>And, um,</i>
<i>that you're a good boy...</i>

18:09.087 --> 18:13.524
and even though you do some things
that we don't like, we still love you.

18:13.591 --> 18:15.718
And I'm watching you.

18:18.763 --> 18:21.323
And I'm cherishing you.

18:26.838 --> 18:29.466
