They were kidnapping me!

19:34.873 --> 19:37.398
Oh, shut up. That's it.
I have had it.

19:37.475 --> 19:39.773
You know what this means?
More discipline.

19:39.844 --> 19:44.474
- No. No.
- Oh, yes. Playtime is over.

19:44.549 --> 19:46.813
Oh, stop saying that.

19:48.453 --> 19:50.512
Your cracking down
is not working.

19:50.588 --> 19:52.453
Hell, I could've
told him that a week ago.

19:54.425 --> 19:57.417
Now is not the time
to be a porky mouth.

19:58.730 --> 20:01.324
Red, I want my house back.

20:03.134 --> 20:06.501
- I once had an ant farm...
- Oh, honey, no. Not now.

20:08.940 --> 20:12.876
